# BPERP — Database schema reference

When you add or rename tables, update this file, `README.md`, `backend/README.md`, and `CHANGELOG.md` as appropriate.

## Core tables

| Table | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| `users` | User accounts with roles, permissions, appearance |
| `user_sessions` | Active auth tokens |
| `role_defaults` | Default permissions per role |
| `user_activity_log` | Audit trail |

## Inventory tables

| Table | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| `products` | Finished assemblies for sale |
| `parts` | Components (purchased or manufactured) |
| `materials` | Raw materials |
| `tooling` | Cutting tools, inserts |
| `misc_items` | Consumables, supplies |

## Sales tables

| Table | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| `customers` | Customer records |
| `customer_contacts` | Contacts per customer |
| `quotes` | Quote header + status workflow |
| `quote_items` | Quote line items |
| `work_orders` | Jobs from won quotes |
| `work_order_parts` | Parts on work orders |

## Production tables

| Table | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| `workcenters` | Work areas (Mill, Lathe, etc.) |
| `machines` | Individual machines |
| `tasks` | Workflow tasks with assignments |
| `maintenance_tasks` | Scheduled maintenance |

## Naming

- DB columns: `snake_case`
- API JSON: `camelCase` (transform in routes)
